          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Monoenergetic photons between 8.8 and 11.4 MeV were",
                " scattered elastically and inelastically (Raman) from",
                " natural targets of Au, Dy, and In. 15 new cross",
                " sections were measured. Evidence is presented for a",
                " slight deformation in the 197Au nucleus, generally",
                " believed to be spherical. It is predicted, on the",
                " basis of these measurements, that the giant dipole",
                " resonance of Dy is very dimilar to that of 160Gd. A",
                " narrow isolated resonance at 9.0 MeV is observed",
                " In."
              ]
            }
          ],
